<li>David J. C. MacKay. <i><a href="http://www.inference.phy.cam.ac.uk/mackay/itila/book.html" class="external text" title="http://www.inference.phy.cam.ac.uk/mackay/itila/book.html" rel="nofollow">Information Theory, Inference, and Learning Algorithms</a></i> Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 2003. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0521642981" class="internal">ISBN 0-521-64298-1</a></li>
